content: I joined a virtual phone bank session but had to leave before the debrief. Is there a debrief survey or anything to fill out?
Hi Maxine - do you know if the zoom was with a particular state party/organization or directly with the Harris-Walz team?

Here is the debrief survey we use for the Harris-Walz phione banks 
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdYNUspIhrNncyYxxznLa2BrGKjI74_T8fMm-nDhImXJtfRrg/viewform

It was directly with the Harris walz team! This was the confirmation text: You're registered with The Democratic Natio... on Sun 10/27 12:00PM EDT. Send this link to friends to invite: https://mobilize.us/s/Ga5DbV/r
Perfect, the debrief I linked above it the right one.  Thank you for making calls with us!
